cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image decomposition, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves generative models (cs.GR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper introduces a new architecture for a convolutional variational autoencoder (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.MM, in that order.
